environmentalDataLogging.entities

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.Client

  • @Entity
public class Client
extends BaseEntity
    The Client entity class is the link to the client table in the EnviroDB database. A Client is a person who sponsors the Environmental Technologies projects.
